title: UFYB 74: 100 Episode Review - A- Work, Let it Be Easy, and Compound Interest

description:
Tune in as I reflect on the biggest gifts podcasting has given me and how I've worked on them to create a successful seven-figure business!

Text your email (all lowercase) to 347-997-1784 and reply with "instagram" when prompted for the secret password to follow me on social media and get links to a couple of articles I wrote!

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfuckyourbrain.com/74
